WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 6=

01:38.180 --> 01:39.850
What's your connection to Qianmian Sect?

01:39.850 --> 01:41.330
Who are you?

01:41.330 --> 01:43.100
I'm Qian Xueshen,

01:43.100 --> 01:45.100
the last descendant of Qianmian Sect.

01:45.290 --> 01:46.210
Please understand.

01:46.620 --> 01:48.050
They forced me to do this.

01:48.050 --> 01:49.690
I'm just a scholar,

01:49.840 --> 01:50.770
with elders and children

01:50.770 --> 01:51.610
to care about.

02:01.180 --> 02:02.020
The Demonic Camp.

02:22.220 --> 02:23.540
Is this is the Chaos Needle?

02:24.570 --> 02:26.570
The victim becomes weak and limp.

02:26.820 --> 02:28.513
But the needle's aura
is extremely strong.

02:29.130 --> 02:30.410
If it weren't someone familiar,

02:30.890 --> 02:32.380
most would be on guard.

02:33.010 --> 02:34.170
To silently take Xingjia away

02:34.260 --> 02:36.780
from the sect shows

02:37.010 --> 02:38.450
that the Demonic Camp's influence

02:39.820 --> 02:41.660
has infiltrated the whole sect.

02:41.980 --> 02:43.890
With Qianmian Sect's Body Shift,

02:44.820 --> 02:45.890
it's not impossible.

02:46.330 --> 02:47.690
The Qianmian Sect is so powerful?

02:48.220 --> 02:49.570
Yet I've never heard of it before.

02:49.850 --> 02:50.890
Long ago,

02:50.980 --> 02:53.220
they were wiped out
by the righteous and demonic sects.

02:53.780 --> 02:55.290
The Qianmian Sect's Body Shift

02:55.890 --> 02:58.450
can alter a person's appearance,

02:59.060 --> 03:00.340
leaving no trace.

03:00.730 --> 03:02.010
Their last lord,

03:02.260 --> 03:03.170
Qianmian Slayer,

03:03.610 --> 03:04.890
used it to cause chaos

03:05.290 --> 03:06.883
and was rejected by the righteous sects.

03:07.220 --> 03:09.226
Later, he brought the sect
to join the demon sect.

03:09.380 --> 03:11.100
But the demon sect exposed

03:11.100 --> 03:12.010
their hideout,

03:12.540 --> 03:14.010
drawing elites from the Six Sects;

03:14.610 --> 03:16.610
thus, the sect was wiped out.

03:17.783 --> 03:19.060
The alliance with the demon sect

03:19.730 --> 03:20.890
was disgraceful,

03:22.023 --> 03:23.663
so the righteous sects
did not record it,

03:23.780 --> 03:24.980
which is why you wouldn't know.

03:27.260 --> 03:28.610
If there are no records,

03:29.130 --> 03:30.780
how did you know?

03:31.260 --> 03:32.100
From Jiuzhou...

03:37.940 --> 03:39.130
Jiuzhou Chronicles.

03:40.290 --> 03:41.130
I never expected

03:42.420 --> 03:43.260
there to be

03:43.260 --> 03:45.010
a descendant of Qianmian Sect.

03:46.660 --> 03:47.500
So,

03:48.130 --> 03:49.850
does the Chronicles record

03:50.940 --> 03:53.100
a way to counter this move?

03:53.616 --> 03:55.146
That is an internal secret of the sect.

03:56.100 --> 03:56.940
I think

03:57.380 --> 03:58.890
only Qian Xueshen would know.

03:59.380 --> 04:00.540
But with all this commotion,

04:00.980 --> 04:02.890
they probably already moved him.

04:06.660 --> 04:07.780
Chang?

04:08.130 --> 04:08.970
Zhao?

04:11.340 --> 04:12.500
Where are we?

04:12.690 --> 04:13.530
Simply put,

04:13.850 --> 04:14.820
you were kidnapped,

04:15.380 --> 04:16.220
but we rescued you.

04:25.050 --> 04:26.580
Why are there butterflies?

04:26.580 --> 04:28.610
I sprinkled pollen on Qian Xueshen.

04:29.140 --> 04:29.980
Let's go find him.

04:40.850 --> 04:42.780
They actually entered Qingque Sect?

04:43.813 --> 04:45.800
Isn't this like sheep walking
into a tiger's den?

04:46.050 --> 04:47.220
Maybe they are the tigers,

04:48.050 --> 04:49.020
and we are the sheep.

05:14.460 --> 05:15.300
Zhao,

05:15.410 --> 05:16.370
I'll go ask around.

05:24.490 --> 05:25.780
The Body Shift has been exposed.

05:26.850 --> 05:28.250
The enemy will surely be on guard.

05:28.730 --> 05:29.730
Returning to the sect now

05:29.980 --> 05:31.050
would be extremely risky.

05:31.250 --> 05:32.100
I know.

05:32.340 --> 05:33.900
But Master's injuries have yet to heal.

05:34.100 --> 05:35.370
I must warn him first.

05:36.490 --> 05:37.540
The situation is perilous.

05:38.020 --> 05:39.170
You should think it through

05:39.703 --> 05:41.430
about whether you want
to risk your life.

05:43.730 --> 05:44.570
Don't worry.

05:44.980 --> 05:46.220
I can handle it myself.

05:46.760 --> 05:47.610
Perhaps this will be

05:47.610 --> 05:48.450
our last meeting.

05:49.050 --> 05:49.930
Let's forget the past.

05:50.276 --> 05:51.330
The martial world is vast.

05:51.610 --> 05:52.460
Take care, Ning.

05:53.826 --> 05:55.930
The lodging fees I owed you
haven't been settled yet.

05:57.086 --> 05:58.340
After helping you one last time,

06:00.220 --> 06:01.250
we'll be even.

06:04.930 --> 06:05.770
Zhao.

06:08.320 --> 06:09.170
What's going on?

06:09.170 --> 06:10.050
The guards said

06:10.540 --> 06:12.490
a few groups entered last night.

06:12.730 --> 06:13.570
But

06:13.730 --> 06:15.140
they all had orders from Master.

06:15.393 --> 06:16.660
Who were those in gray just now?

06:16.700 --> 06:17.930
They are the reinforcements

06:18.290 --> 06:19.490
I mentioned before.

06:19.850 --> 06:20.810
All Qingque lords

06:20.850 --> 06:22.490
cultivate some martial artists

06:22.613 --> 06:23.700
to call upon in emergencies.

06:24.050 --> 06:25.410
They are commanded by the Lord;

06:25.410 --> 06:26.810
even Uncle Li can't control them.

06:42.850 --> 06:43.690
Milady.

06:44.050 --> 06:44.890
Zhao,

06:45.290 --> 06:47.050
I heard you searched for Fan all night.

06:47.170 --> 06:48.010
Is everything okay?

06:48.290 --> 06:50.100
(Weak inner energy. She's real.)

06:50.370 --> 06:51.210
It's fine.

06:51.220 --> 06:52.170
Just a little trouble.

06:52.660 --> 06:53.500
It's all resolved.

06:56.460 --> 06:57.300
Zhuo,

06:58.490 --> 07:00.220
have you finished the Sober Powder

07:00.510 --> 07:01.360
Feicui made for you?

07:01.370 --> 07:02.320
It wasn't me.

07:03.540 --> 07:05.170
It was your mother.

07:05.580 --> 07:06.420
I've finished it.

07:06.700 --> 07:07.620
Yeah, it was my mother.

07:08.100 --> 07:08.940
That's good.

07:09.700 --> 07:10.540
Xingjia,

07:10.710 --> 07:12.259
why didn't you tell us before you left?

07:12.730 --> 07:13.810
I wanted to,

07:13.980 --> 07:15.980
but I was sleeping in my room.

07:16.170 --> 07:17.667
I woke up and find myself in the town,

07:17.730 --> 07:18.930
almost losing my life.

07:19.660 --> 07:20.730
Someone took Xingjia away

07:20.930 --> 07:22.730
without anyone noticing.

07:23.050 --> 07:24.100
It means many intruders

07:25.220 --> 07:26.700
must have infiltrated the sect.

07:36.020 --> 07:36.980
Master is in seclusion.

07:37.610 --> 07:38.580
No one may see him

07:39.610 --> 07:40.450
except for Dalou.

07:41.730 --> 07:42.980
Why not talk to Uncle Li?

07:43.490 --> 07:44.700
I just went to the kitchen

07:45.020 --> 07:46.616
and saw Uncle Li Wenxun

07:46.627 --> 07:47.810
talking to some guards in gray

07:47.810 --> 07:49.050
whom I've never seen.

07:49.490 --> 07:51.780
He even told the cooks
to take care of them.

07:58.410 --> 07:59.780
It's best not to alert anyone yet.

08:02.810 --> 08:03.650
Xiaolan,

08:04.020 --> 08:05.610
check around with Zhuo.

08:06.250 --> 08:07.490
Look for suspicious people.

08:09.340 --> 08:10.180
Ning,

08:11.140 --> 08:13.020
go find Qian Xueshen with Xingjia.

08:13.700 --> 08:14.540
What about you?

08:15.900 --> 08:16.780
Master will see me.

08:25.706 --> 08:26.930
The Lord is in seclusion today,

08:27.250 --> 08:28.090
not seeing anyone.

08:31.580 --> 08:32.730
Please tell Master

08:33.420 --> 08:34.700
that I have an urgent matter.

08:34.890 --> 08:35.910
The Lord won't see anyone.

08:36.130 --> 08:36.882
Did you hear that?

08:36.893 --> 08:38.575
My father said
he doesn't want to see you.

08:38.586 --> 08:39.180
Leave.

08:40.113 --> 08:41.370
The Lord is in seclusion today,

08:41.580 --> 08:42.420
not seeing anyone.

08:42.940 --> 08:45.100
I brought soup to my father.

08:45.220 --> 08:46.750
He will see me. Let me through.

08:46.770 --> 08:47.820
The Lord won't see anyone.

08:49.890 --> 08:50.730
Forget it, Lingbo.

08:51.340 --> 08:52.530
I suppose these two

08:52.530 --> 08:53.730
are acting on Master's orders.

08:54.370 --> 08:55.370
It seems Master

08:55.940 --> 08:56.893
doesn't want to see you.

08:57.536 --> 08:58.610
What does it matter to you?

09:01.610 --> 09:02.700
It's a pity

09:02.980 --> 09:04.530
no one will drink the soup

09:05.700 --> 09:07.060
you carefully prepared.

09:10.530 --> 09:12.010
I'll go in today.

09:12.010 --> 09:12.850
Let me through.

09:12.980 --> 09:13.820
Miss Qi.

09:16.730 --> 09:17.850
You two!

09:17.980 --> 09:18.683
How could you?

09:18.694 --> 09:19.890
Give me back my chicken soup!

09:19.890 --> 09:21.060
My chicken soup!

09:21.060 --> 09:22.060
Give it back!

09:22.420 --> 09:23.300
My chicken soup!

09:23.300 --> 09:24.409
How dare you touch

09:24.420 --> 09:26.180
- my chicken soup?
- It's the Lord's order.

09:32.010 --> 09:32.850
Zhao.

09:33.460 --> 09:35.060
Master, are you alright?

09:35.100 --> 09:35.940
Don't come closer.

09:37.460 --> 09:38.460
I'm fine.

09:40.370 --> 09:42.650
Did you come for something urgent?

09:42.980 --> 09:43.890
Last night, Xingjia

09:44.460 --> 09:46.460
was taken away by the Demonic Camp.

09:47.180 --> 09:48.020
Understood.

09:49.610 --> 09:50.700
Dalou, let me through.

09:50.700 --> 09:51.540
Lingbo,

09:51.650 --> 09:52.490
you can't enter.

09:52.940 --> 09:54.220
When did you come in?

09:54.850 --> 09:55.690
While you

09:55.879 --> 09:57.073
were killing your way through.

09:57.340 --> 09:58.460
You used me!

09:59.700 --> 10:00.540
Father,

10:00.836 --> 10:01.730
she caused me to spill

10:02.060 --> 10:04.060
the chicken soup I made for you.

10:04.189 --> 10:05.290
She even provoked me to act.

10:05.340 --> 10:06.220
Who let you come here?

10:06.980 --> 10:07.820
Everyone, out.

10:08.130 --> 10:09.060
Father.

10:09.460 --> 10:10.300
Yunke,

10:10.610 --> 10:13.100
are you kicking me out, too?

10:13.340 --> 10:14.180
Lady Yin,

10:14.460 --> 10:16.010
Master is recovering from injury.

10:16.021 --> 10:17.379
It's not the time to be distracted.

10:17.390 --> 10:18.220
Please leave.

10:18.770 --> 10:19.610
Father,

10:21.250 --> 10:22.890
you've been in seclusion
for a long time.

10:22.940 --> 10:24.250
You haven't seen Mother and Yuzhi

10:24.340 --> 10:25.830
- for so long.
- Lingbo.

10:25.850 --> 10:26.720
Shut up!

10:26.720 --> 10:27.570
Zeng Dalou!

10:37.100 --> 10:37.940
Lady Yin,

10:38.460 --> 10:40.130
Master's poisoning injury is severe.

10:40.423 --> 10:41.443
It can't be taken lightly.

10:41.610 --> 10:42.980
Please understand.

10:46.700 --> 10:47.540
Yunke,

10:48.820 --> 10:49.660
I'm your wife.

10:50.300 --> 10:51.580
If something is wrong,

10:52.180 --> 10:53.300
you should tell me.

10:53.580 --> 10:54.420
Dear,

10:54.980 --> 10:55.850
don't worry.

10:56.980 --> 10:58.420
When my injuries heal,

10:58.850 --> 10:59.770
I'll go see you.

11:00.890 --> 11:02.180
You all should leave first.

11:06.890 --> 11:07.730
Mother.

11:08.890 --> 11:10.350
- Mother.
- Master,

11:10.370 --> 11:11.210
I take my leave.

11:13.180 --> 11:14.020
Master,

11:14.490 --> 11:16.250
I'll leave first.

11:16.770 --> 11:17.610
Sure.

11:25.300 --> 11:26.140
Master,

11:26.636 --> 11:27.890
this is a glazed lantern, right?

11:28.580 --> 11:30.490
You gave me one when I was nine.

11:30.730 --> 11:31.610
I liked it very much.

11:31.770 --> 11:32.820
If you like it,

11:33.300 --> 11:34.180
take it.

11:35.580 --> 11:36.890
Now, it makes a pair.

11:39.250 --> 11:40.130
Thank you, Master.

11:44.940 --> 11:46.130
You're really kind to me.

11:56.180 --> 11:57.020
What?

11:57.130 --> 11:58.530
Master is fake, too?

11:59.250 --> 12:00.090
Lower your voice.

12:00.650 --> 12:01.490
What?

12:01.700 --> 12:03.060
Master is fake, too?

12:03.060 --> 12:03.900
When I was nine,

12:03.931 --> 12:05.859
the path in Luoying Valley
was slippery in snow.

12:05.890 --> 12:06.850
Master fell,

12:07.220 --> 12:08.370
and the lantern broke.

12:09.460 --> 12:11.220
Master blamed himself for a long time.

12:11.530 --> 12:12.460
If Master were real,

12:13.610 --> 12:14.610
he'd know the lantern

12:14.610 --> 12:16.100
can't make a pair again.

12:18.530 --> 12:19.370
Zhuo,

12:20.386 --> 12:21.746
have you noticed anyone suspicious?

12:21.940 --> 12:23.033
Besides the people in gray,

12:24.250 --> 12:25.090
there's no evidence.

12:26.733 --> 12:27.660
What about you, Xingjia?

12:27.730 --> 12:28.980
Any clue about Qian Xueshen?

12:29.650 --> 12:30.759
I searched the water prison,

12:30.770 --> 12:32.300
dungeon, dry prison,

12:32.311 --> 12:33.210
and the back storeroom

12:33.250 --> 12:35.340
of the Disciples' Dorm.

12:35.420 --> 12:36.260
No one at all.

12:36.850 --> 12:39.130
Could it be
the Trace Butterfly misled us?

12:40.420 --> 12:41.260
I don't think so.

12:44.460 --> 12:46.370
Ning, you know the sect well.

12:47.490 --> 12:48.340
Do you know

12:49.010 --> 12:50.230
where else someone could hide?

12:54.100 --> 12:55.370
I heard Lord Yin Dai

12:56.730 --> 12:58.010
built a secret prison.

12:58.490 --> 13:00.580
It's extremely hidden.

13:00.850 --> 13:01.890
Only a few know.

13:02.420 --> 13:03.260
Unless...

13:13.610 --> 13:14.530
Thanks, Yuzhi.

13:17.010 --> 13:18.890
I know you are severely injured

13:18.890 --> 13:20.170
and must be on guard constantly.

13:20.650 --> 13:21.840
But isn't it

13:22.420 --> 13:23.580
a bit excessive?

13:26.820 --> 13:27.660
Uncle Pang.

13:27.660 --> 13:28.900
(Pang Xiongxin, Guangtian Sect)

13:40.220 --> 13:41.700
You act like facing a great enemy.

13:42.340 --> 13:44.460
Do you find something off?

13:50.820 --> 13:52.940
Xingjia was almost switched yesterday.

13:53.250 --> 13:55.770
I hope you'll be honest with me.

14:01.060 --> 14:02.130
Lately, Master

14:02.730 --> 14:03.770
hasn't visited me

14:04.340 --> 14:05.700
or met Lady Yin.

14:06.300 --> 14:07.850
Master always doted on Lady Yin.

14:08.130 --> 14:09.940
No matter how she angered him before,

14:10.250 --> 14:12.010
he would never be so heartless.

14:12.820 --> 14:13.700
As expected.

14:14.890 --> 14:15.730
Yuzhi,

14:17.460 --> 14:18.490
have you heard

14:19.490 --> 14:21.100
of the Body Shift?

14:24.420 --> 14:25.260
Chang!

14:29.423 --> 14:30.523
She's been gone for so long.

14:30.850 --> 14:32.010
If Song Yuzhi is fake,

14:32.650 --> 14:33.650
Zhao could be in danger.

14:33.820 --> 14:35.420
Yuzhi was poisoned by Nether Aura.

14:35.460 --> 14:36.460
The aura can't be faked.

14:37.180 --> 14:38.890
See? You're just too worried.

14:39.220 --> 14:40.060
Let's wait a bit.

14:42.180 --> 14:43.020
Chang.

14:43.730 --> 14:44.570
Chang!

14:45.060 --> 14:46.980
I always felt this sect attack

14:46.980 --> 14:47.850
was strange.

14:49.770 --> 14:50.770
So, they aimed at Master

14:50.770 --> 14:51.890
from the start.

14:53.890 --> 14:55.209
Master's martial power is supreme.

14:55.220 --> 14:56.060
He's hard to imitate.

14:56.460 --> 14:58.530
The only way the impostor

14:58.940 --> 14:59.940
could avoid detection

15:00.820 --> 15:01.770
is to go into seclusion.

15:02.413 --> 15:03.420
Where is the real Master?

15:03.420 --> 15:04.650
Master is a lord.

15:05.010 --> 15:06.223
For such an important hostage,

15:06.580 --> 15:08.340
until they achieve their goal,

15:08.490 --> 15:09.700
they will keep him alive.

15:13.220 --> 15:14.530
We must not act rashly,

15:15.250 --> 15:17.130
lest they panic and kill
to cover their tracks.

15:17.530 --> 15:19.060
We should first find Qian Xueshen

15:19.060 --> 15:20.473
and ask about Master's whereabouts.

15:20.650 --> 15:21.490
Yuzhi,

15:22.100 --> 15:23.940
do you know if there's a secret prison

15:24.940 --> 15:26.010
in Qingque Sect?

15:27.180 --> 15:28.020
Secret prison?

15:29.700 --> 15:31.340
My grandfather did have one.

15:32.920 --> 15:33.770
This secret prison

15:33.770 --> 15:35.610
was where Elder Kaiyang was held.

15:35.850 --> 15:37.010
It's under the Library,

15:37.340 --> 15:38.180
but now abandoned.

15:45.340 --> 15:46.180
Let's go.

15:48.650 --> 15:49.890
Yuzhi, with your injuries,

15:50.100 --> 15:51.530
you should stay here and keep watch.

15:52.130 --> 15:52.970
I'm going.

15:53.100 --> 15:53.940
Zhao,

15:54.396 --> 15:56.910
the secret prison is dangerous
after being abandoned for years.

15:56.980 --> 15:58.370
I must go with you.

16:00.060 --> 16:01.830
You're so weak.

16:02.010 --> 16:03.100
What good will that do?

16:04.940 --> 16:07.010
Not everything relies on brute force.

16:12.980 --> 16:14.060
Both of you, stop arguing.

16:14.460 --> 16:15.700
Zhao is going down.

16:16.650 --> 16:17.820
I'll stay and keep watch.

16:34.300 --> 16:36.346
Back then, Lu Chengnan,
Leader of the Demonic Camp,

16:36.460 --> 16:37.610
once infiltrated Qingque Sect

16:37.610 --> 16:39.010
and tried to seize Elder Kaiyang.

16:39.300 --> 16:41.770
Surely, there was a fierce battle here.

16:42.060 --> 16:44.490
Lord Yin hid Elder Kaiyang deeply.

16:44.610 --> 16:46.130
It seems he's determined

16:46.220 --> 16:47.093
to get what he wanted.

16:47.180 --> 16:48.400
The demon sect acted cunningly.

16:48.490 --> 16:50.060
My grandfather was to prevent trouble.

16:57.340 --> 16:58.610
Are you two here to argue,

16:58.610 --> 16:59.460
or to help?

17:03.460 --> 17:04.300
In a critical moment,

17:04.770 --> 17:05.870
won't brute force be needed?

17:13.290 --> 17:16.220
Don't kill me!

17:18.140 --> 17:18.980
It's me.

17:19.980 --> 17:20.820
It's you.

17:21.050 --> 17:21.980
How did you find me?

17:21.980 --> 17:22.820
Enough talk.

17:28.146 --> 17:29.330
Song, don't waste your effort.

17:29.470 --> 17:31.220
These iron chains
likely contain black iron.

17:31.220 --> 17:32.660
Normal weapons can't cut them.

17:33.700 --> 17:34.540
I think

17:34.999 --> 17:36.335
we should just chop off his hands.

17:36.420 --> 17:37.660
No! Spare me, please!

17:37.660 --> 17:39.330
I was also captured.

17:39.380 --> 17:40.620
It's not my fault!

17:42.490 --> 17:43.703
Among the people you disguised,

17:43.940 --> 17:45.660
was there a Qingque Lord?

17:45.660 --> 17:47.460
I never leave my house.

17:47.700 --> 17:49.570
How would I know who the Lord is?

17:49.730 --> 17:50.660
Around 40 years old,

17:51.220 --> 17:52.060
handsome,

17:52.380 --> 17:53.220
with a beard.

17:53.250 --> 17:54.090
He might be poisoned

17:54.146 --> 17:55.192
but has deep internal power

17:55.250 --> 17:56.203
and strange meridians,

17:56.380 --> 17:57.460
beyond ordinary people.

17:57.810 --> 17:59.380
I think there is such a person.

18:01.220 --> 18:02.060
Where is he?

18:02.860 --> 18:04.570
I changed his face in Qingque Town;

18:05.250 --> 18:06.420
then he was taken away.

18:06.420 --> 18:07.460
I don't know where he went,

18:07.730 --> 18:09.620
but anyone taken is important.

18:09.660 --> 18:10.980
They usually don't hurry to kill.

18:11.090 --> 18:12.330
How to counter the Body Shift?

18:14.010 --> 18:16.140
My Body Shift

18:16.380 --> 18:17.380
is exquisite.

18:17.570 --> 18:18.660
There's no solution.

18:19.860 --> 18:20.810
If so,

18:21.220 --> 18:22.090
then you're useless.

18:22.660 --> 18:23.700
I can help you.

18:23.860 --> 18:24.700
There is a way!

18:24.860 --> 18:25.940
Once the person dies,

18:26.570 --> 18:27.410
the effect ends.

18:27.620 --> 18:29.620
Saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

18:30.730 --> 18:31.730
Snow-Scale Beast?

18:33.860 --> 18:34.700
Where?

18:37.250 --> 18:38.730
Head straight north

18:39.172 --> 18:40.991
into the snow mountains
in the Freezing Area.

18:41.490 --> 18:43.140
I've told you everything I know.

18:43.330 --> 18:44.330
If you want to save him,

18:44.420 --> 18:45.490
hurry to get the saliva.

18:45.730 --> 18:46.980
Once the fake takes control,

18:47.700 --> 18:49.330
the real one will be near death.

18:50.140 --> 18:51.010
We'll get you out,

18:51.220 --> 18:52.293
lest you harm anyone again.

18:55.986 --> 18:57.626
This is the sect's alarm bell
for danger.

18:57.700 --> 18:58.600
We've been discovered.

18:59.460 --> 19:00.013
Good.

19:00.100 --> 19:01.929
Let's take him out
and confront the impostor.

19:01.940 --> 19:04.330
No, how can you claim
the Lord is fake

19:04.713 --> 19:05.860
with an unknown Qian Xueshen?

19:05.860 --> 19:06.700
It's the only way.

19:06.940 --> 19:07.780
Breaking into here,

19:07.956 --> 19:09.290
we can't handle it peacefully now.

19:09.660 --> 19:11.290
Why not make a commotion?

19:11.460 --> 19:12.730
This way,

19:12.940 --> 19:13.780
they'll take notice,

19:14.090 --> 19:15.570
and we can buy time for Master,

19:15.900 --> 19:16.880
keeping him safe for now.

19:17.940 --> 19:18.780
Yuzhi,

19:18.940 --> 19:19.780
you stay here.

19:19.800 --> 19:20.980
If I can't get out,

19:21.140 --> 19:22.810
you must go to retrieve the saliva

19:23.570 --> 19:24.410
and save Master.

19:25.090 --> 19:25.930
Understood.

19:26.180 --> 19:27.020
Be careful.

19:27.570 --> 19:28.460
No one will believe

19:28.460 --> 19:30.050
the Lord of the top sect is fake.

19:31.380 --> 19:32.330
No one will believe you.

19:35.180 --> 19:37.340
(Dusk Palace)

19:37.810 --> 19:40.330
(Righteous Spirit)
The demonic sect is attacking us.

19:41.570 --> 19:43.530
I've been investigating.

19:43.770 --> 19:45.570
And I've received news.

19:51.993 --> 19:53.232
The demonic sect found someone

19:53.330 --> 19:55.570
from Qianmian Sect.

19:57.090 --> 19:59.700
To avoid a jailbreak
by the demonic sect,

20:00.490 --> 20:02.700
the Lord locked him in the dark prison

20:03.220 --> 20:05.250
and set up

20:06.330 --> 20:08.180
warning mechanisms.

20:09.250 --> 20:10.090
Master,

20:10.380 --> 20:11.220
Uncle Li,

20:11.860 --> 20:13.730
Qian Xueshen almost replaced me.

20:13.900 --> 20:14.980
Zhao and Chang

20:14.980 --> 20:16.490
also worried about the demon sect

20:16.700 --> 20:18.616
might have switched someone else,

20:18.627 --> 20:19.980
so they entered the secret prison

20:20.010 --> 20:21.660
to find the antidote to the Body Shift.

20:21.730 --> 20:22.570
Xingjia,

20:22.660 --> 20:24.700
did you witness Qian Xueshen

20:24.700 --> 20:26.330
using the Body Shift?

20:26.620 --> 20:27.460
I...

20:30.980 --> 20:32.010
When I woke up,

20:32.860 --> 20:33.860
he had been taken away.

20:34.090 --> 20:35.620
You didn't see it;

20:36.140 --> 20:38.050
that's just their side of the story.

20:38.460 --> 20:39.900
Demon sect members are cunning.

20:40.290 --> 20:41.420
We can't believe it blindly.

20:42.620 --> 20:43.810
Take him away.

20:43.860 --> 20:44.770
Keep him imprisoned.

20:45.220 --> 20:46.500
- Yes.
- Wait.

20:54.660 --> 20:55.770
Among those present,

20:56.250 --> 20:57.460
aside from Qian Xueshen,

21:00.250 --> 21:01.940
there is another one
of the demonic sect.

21:05.220 --> 21:06.060
Who?

21:13.330 --> 21:14.330
Ning.

21:15.700 --> 21:17.460
Does the Jiuzhou Archive
of the demonic sect

21:18.090 --> 21:20.330
really hold books as vast as the sea?

21:22.770 --> 21:23.610
Zhao,

21:24.140 --> 21:25.140
what are you saying?

21:25.620 --> 21:27.570
You schemed to infiltrate Qingque Sect

21:28.250 --> 21:29.490
just to gain my trust.

21:30.220 --> 21:32.090
Then you helped Ms. Luo come here.

21:34.810 --> 21:36.290
During the memorial chaos,

21:36.653 --> 21:37.799
you left Wu Gang and Wu Xiong

21:37.810 --> 21:38.996
to coordinate inside the sect.

21:39.900 --> 21:41.840
You even killed the guards
at Thousandfold Cliff,

21:42.090 --> 21:43.330
helping the demon sect attack,

21:46.380 --> 21:48.490
causing Master to be injured

21:48.570 --> 21:49.770
and go into seclusion,

21:50.290 --> 21:51.900
so your replacement plan

21:52.250 --> 21:53.620
would succeed without fail.

21:55.900 --> 21:56.740
Chang Ning,

21:57.660 --> 21:58.860
you are a demon sect spy!

21:58.900 --> 22:00.180
Seize this spy!

22:02.810 --> 22:03.650
Stop!

22:12.530 --> 22:13.380
- Zhao!
- Zhao!

22:13.380 --> 22:14.220
Dalou!

22:14.330 --> 22:15.770
Cai Zhao, are you mad?

22:15.940 --> 22:17.250
If I kill the wrong person today,

22:18.050 --> 22:19.420
I'll give my life to repay his.

22:19.620 --> 22:20.460
You...

23:05.570 --> 23:07.170
Look, Dalou has changed.

23:15.620 --> 23:16.940
So, there really is a Body Shift.

23:19.250 --> 23:20.810
Then who is this person?

23:22.140 --> 23:23.220
Where is the real Dalou?

23:25.290 --> 23:26.130
When the person dies,

23:27.090 --> 23:28.180
the Body Shift ends.

23:28.770 --> 23:30.490
This is the spy impersonating Dalou.

23:31.700 --> 23:32.810
The real Dalou

23:33.570 --> 23:35.290
is hidden somewhere unknown.

23:36.820 --> 23:37.670
I don't know.

23:37.700 --> 23:38.620
I know nothing.

23:40.090 --> 23:41.380
The only person present

23:41.860 --> 23:43.980
who knows where Dalou is

23:44.810 --> 23:45.810
is Master.

23:46.900 --> 23:48.050
Because you are also fake.

23:48.220 --> 23:49.060
Zhao,

23:52.660 --> 23:54.050
for your aunt's sake,

23:54.380 --> 23:56.010
your mischief is normally forgiven,

23:56.290 --> 23:58.290
but accusations can't be made randomly.

23:58.900 --> 23:59.740
Dear,

24:00.250 --> 24:01.850
Zhao was deceived

24:02.180 --> 24:03.860
by the demon sect.

24:04.380 --> 24:06.700
She's inexperienced and naive.

24:06.980 --> 24:08.660
She's just used without realizing it.

24:09.620 --> 24:10.570
Qian Xueshen,

24:10.980 --> 24:12.380
you did the job. Say it.

24:14.810 --> 24:15.650
I...

24:17.860 --> 24:18.940
The one I swapped

24:19.530 --> 24:20.370
was poisoned

24:21.090 --> 24:22.290
and highly skilled.

24:23.380 --> 24:24.220
That's him.

24:28.980 --> 24:29.980
Demon sect members

24:30.380 --> 24:31.860
swapped a few of our own

24:32.250 --> 24:34.050
to create distrust among us.

24:34.490 --> 24:35.330
Zhao,

24:35.700 --> 24:37.490
you fell for their trick.

24:38.330 --> 24:39.170
Zhao,

24:39.220 --> 24:40.810
your master usually dotes on you.

24:41.530 --> 24:43.460
How could you frame him

24:43.490 --> 24:44.460
with demon sect spies?

24:44.860 --> 24:45.700
Lady Yin,

24:46.380 --> 24:48.900
Master always used
his injuries as an excuse,

24:49.220 --> 24:50.940
ignoring years of marital affection,

24:51.660 --> 24:53.010
and avoided you,

24:53.250 --> 24:54.490
yet you doubted him not at all?

25:01.490 --> 25:03.050
Our marital bond

25:03.620 --> 25:05.700
is not for juniors to meddle in.

25:06.140 --> 25:08.700
Wenxun, Cai Zhao is obstinate.
Seize her.

25:26.860 --> 25:28.100
- Father!
- Yunke!

25:28.100 --> 25:28.950
I'm fine.

25:28.950 --> 25:29.800
Li Wenxun!

25:30.660 --> 25:31.500
Wenxun,

25:32.140 --> 25:33.570
can you now prove it?

25:38.460 --> 25:39.300
Cai Zhao,

25:39.476 --> 25:40.460
appearances can be faked,

25:40.980 --> 25:42.220
but martial skills can't.

25:44.490 --> 25:45.860
As everyone saw,

25:46.330 --> 25:47.250
the Lord indeed used

25:47.570 --> 25:48.980
our mindful way.

25:49.700 --> 25:51.010
We can't believe just one account.

25:52.330 --> 25:53.180
I've verified

25:53.530 --> 25:54.370
that the Body Shift

25:54.490 --> 25:55.330
threatens the sect.

25:55.810 --> 25:56.876
Since you don't believe me,

25:57.250 --> 25:58.250
do as you will

25:59.180 --> 26:00.050
from now on.

26:00.660 --> 26:01.600
I'm leaving immediately.

26:02.220 --> 26:03.226
It's none of my business.

26:06.010 --> 26:06.850
Let's go.

26:07.070 --> 26:07.910
Wenxun,

26:07.940 --> 26:08.780
stop her.

26:08.940 --> 26:10.290
She can't take Qian Xueshen away.

26:18.050 --> 26:18.890
Wenxun.

26:19.380 --> 26:21.290
What's happening here?

26:22.140 --> 26:22.980
Yunke,

26:23.700 --> 26:25.570
as the Lord of Qingque Sect,

26:25.570 --> 26:27.010
why are you opposing juniors?

26:27.330 --> 26:28.380
If you hurt Zhao

26:28.380 --> 26:29.220
by accident,

26:29.250 --> 26:30.330
what should we do?

26:30.980 --> 26:31.820
Shijun,

26:32.050 --> 26:33.010
you don't know.

26:33.460 --> 26:35.570
Qian Xueshen is from Qianmian Sect.

26:36.090 --> 26:37.380
If he enters Jianghu,

26:37.490 --> 26:38.620
he will cause great trouble.

26:39.140 --> 26:40.380
You need not interfere.

26:41.250 --> 26:42.090
That won't do.

26:42.380 --> 26:44.770
Our members have always been upright.

26:45.290 --> 26:46.460
If the righteous qi

26:46.700 --> 26:48.050
in my dantian

26:48.050 --> 26:49.010
is released,

26:49.420 --> 26:50.260
it will burst out.

26:50.860 --> 26:52.380
We can't suppress it.

26:52.940 --> 26:53.940
So,

26:53.940 --> 26:54.810
I must intervene.

26:54.810 --> 26:55.650
Let's go.

26:58.140 --> 26:59.230
Wenxun, stop them!

26:59.250 --> 27:00.140
They can't leave!

27:00.770 --> 27:01.620
They won't.

27:01.620 --> 27:02.460
They won't leave.

27:02.980 --> 27:05.290
The mountains are filled with my men.

27:05.770 --> 27:08.180
I just worry about you.

27:08.530 --> 27:10.290
I heard you were attacked

27:10.420 --> 27:11.700
and badly injured.

27:12.420 --> 27:13.260
I'm so worried.

27:13.330 --> 27:16.050
You must take care of your health now.

27:33.810 --> 27:35.456
We're really going
to the snow mountains?

27:35.770 --> 27:36.610
If you stay,

27:36.980 --> 27:37.980
you'll surely die.

27:38.530 --> 27:39.370
Come with me.

27:39.526 --> 27:41.119
Maybe there's still a chance to survive.

27:43.940 --> 27:44.780
Zhao.

27:47.820 --> 27:48.670
Yuzhi?

27:48.700 --> 27:50.010
The Body Shift is now public.

27:50.170 --> 27:51.700
The Guangtian Sect will guard strictly.

27:51.700 --> 27:53.063
The impostor dares not act rashly.

27:53.180 --> 27:54.020
In time,

27:54.090 --> 27:55.730
Lord Cai and Lord Zhou will arrive.

27:55.900 --> 27:57.730
Once the truth is out,
Master will be found.

27:57.900 --> 27:58.740
You don't have to go.

28:02.770 --> 28:03.943
The Body Shift has no flaw.

28:03.954 --> 28:05.889
The impostor even knows
our sect's mindful ways.

28:05.900 --> 28:06.940
Should I let my father

28:07.230 --> 28:08.620
commit a grave injustice to kill him

28:08.940 --> 28:09.890
to verify his identity?

28:11.730 --> 28:12.570
No.

28:12.660 --> 28:14.090
He is the Lord of the top sect.

28:14.810 --> 28:16.620
If we can't expose him publicly,

28:16.730 --> 28:17.890
how can we break the deadlock?

28:18.140 --> 28:18.936
Waiting another day

28:18.947 --> 28:20.479
means another day of danger for Master.

28:20.490 --> 28:22.730
Rather than wait in fear and doubt,

28:22.900 --> 28:24.570
we should go to retrieve the saliva.

28:24.900 --> 28:26.033
Maybe there's still a chance.

28:26.570 --> 28:28.050
The horses and luggage are ready.

28:28.810 --> 28:29.650
Take care, Zhao.

28:31.290 --> 28:32.130
Zhao!

28:33.980 --> 28:35.500
- Xiaolan?
- Zhao,

28:36.180 --> 28:38.250
with my poor skills, I can't help much.

28:38.420 --> 28:40.380
Here's some money I've saved,

28:40.380 --> 28:41.533
always useful when traveling.

28:42.140 --> 28:43.620
Xiaolan,

28:44.490 --> 28:45.330
don't worry.

28:45.380 --> 28:47.050
Yuzhi has prepared the money.

28:48.290 --> 28:49.480
No, it's different.

28:50.050 --> 28:51.250
Zhao, don't worry.

28:51.330 --> 28:52.170
Take it.

28:53.180 --> 28:54.290
Then I'll take it.

28:54.980 --> 28:56.290
I'll definitely practice hard

28:56.730 --> 28:58.380
and stay with Yuzhi to guard here,

28:58.620 --> 28:59.580
waiting for your return.

28:59.900 --> 29:00.740
Wait for me.

29:14.490 --> 29:16.023
The Lord has gone into seclusion again.

29:16.380 --> 29:18.980
Lord Song sealed
the iron chain mechanisms.

29:19.530 --> 29:22.420
No one may enter or leave now.

29:23.050 --> 29:23.890
Nanny Mao,

29:24.980 --> 29:25.900
could it be

29:26.460 --> 29:27.490
that he's indeed fake?

29:32.180 --> 29:35.140
Double Lotus Palace is closed
starting today.

29:35.900 --> 29:36.980
All we can do

29:38.940 --> 29:40.490
is wait for the result.

29:41.220 --> 29:42.060
Where's Cai Zhao?

29:43.460 --> 29:44.940
She left.

30:31.980 --> 30:33.220
Miss Cai.

30:33.660 --> 30:35.290
- Nature calls.
- Nature calls.

30:38.660 --> 30:39.980
I need to release myself.

30:42.250 --> 30:43.090
My stomach...

30:43.420 --> 30:44.330
You can't escape.

30:47.570 --> 30:48.410
I'm not running.

30:56.530 --> 30:57.490
Ghost!

30:57.570 --> 30:58.410
Ghost!

31:00.140 --> 31:00.980
A seductive ghost!

31:02.220 --> 31:03.060
A seductive ghost!

31:13.090 --> 31:14.180
Seductive...

31:15.773 --> 31:16.853
Where's the seductive ghost?

31:17.770 --> 31:18.770
It was just here.

31:20.050 --> 31:20.890
Seductive ghost!

31:30.180 --> 31:31.020
Zhao.

31:32.730 --> 31:34.420
Does this ghost know you?

31:38.490 --> 31:39.490
May I ask...

31:39.530 --> 31:40.370
My name is

31:40.770 --> 31:41.730
Mu Qingyan.

31:43.050 --> 31:44.220
I've been waiting here

31:44.420 --> 31:46.010
for you for a day and a night.

31:48.050 --> 31:49.460
Trying to scare me?

32:20.050 --> 32:20.980
(Chang Ning?)

32:20.980 --> 32:22.660
(Mu Qingyan, Young Master of Li Sect)

32:31.810 --> 32:32.650
Zhao,

32:33.620 --> 32:34.673
what do you mean by this?

32:34.946 --> 32:37.046
Luoying Valley and the demon sect
are sworn enemies,

32:37.180 --> 32:38.620
let alone their young master.

33:12.870 --> 33:13.730
Go!

33:13.730 --> 33:15.810
If Mr. Qian doesn't take my antidote,

33:15.940 --> 33:16.780
he will die suddenly

33:17.010 --> 33:18.420
by tonight.

33:21.700 --> 33:22.540
Mu Qingyan,

33:22.940 --> 33:23.980
what exactly do you want?

33:26.530 --> 33:27.570
The wonton is ready

33:29.140 --> 33:30.290
to go into the pot.

33:48.860 --> 33:49.770
What antidote?

33:50.460 --> 33:51.420
Back in the dungeon,

33:51.420 --> 33:53.730
I accidentally fed him
a Chasing Pill,

33:54.330 --> 33:56.810
also called a Seizing Pill.

33:56.900 --> 33:58.530
You set a trap in the dungeon?

34:00.090 --> 34:01.250
Didn't you plot against me

34:01.250 --> 34:02.180
in the dungeon?

34:04.180 --> 34:05.050
No one will believe

34:05.050 --> 34:06.660
the Lord of the top sect is fake.

34:07.860 --> 34:08.900
No one will believe you.

34:13.780 --> 34:14.650
I have a plan.

34:15.780 --> 34:16.620
I'll do it with you.

34:18.650 --> 34:19.490
We're even.

34:20.610 --> 34:21.450
Give me the antidote.

34:21.780 --> 34:22.620
No rush.

34:23.610 --> 34:25.130
Try this pickled bamboo shoots first.

34:25.460 --> 34:26.460
Uncle Chang taught me.

34:26.900 --> 34:27.740
Luzhou style.

34:28.050 --> 34:29.010
Perfect

34:29.050 --> 34:29.890
with wonton.

34:30.050 --> 34:31.363
Uncle Chang has always hated evil

34:31.820 --> 34:33.570
and never aligned with the demon sect.

34:34.260 --> 34:35.100
I don't understand

34:35.780 --> 34:36.740
why he'd help you.

34:37.860 --> 34:38.700
Probably

34:40.050 --> 34:41.420
because I'm a good person.

34:42.980 --> 34:44.210
Before, in Dusk Palace,

34:44.420 --> 34:45.610
you put me in great danger,

34:46.090 --> 34:47.423
yet I still treated you to wonton.

34:47.610 --> 34:49.003
Doesn't that make me a good person?

34:50.210 --> 34:51.050
Enough.

34:51.650 --> 34:52.780
I know you'll escape.

34:52.980 --> 34:54.300
As the Young Master of Li Sect,

34:55.130 --> 34:57.050
my father was close to Mr. Chang.

34:57.900 --> 34:58.740
Back then,

34:58.860 --> 35:01.690
Mr. Chang got lost
while attacking Youming Path

35:02.420 --> 35:03.570
with the Six Sects.

35:04.010 --> 35:06.010
He ran into my father raising a Peng.

35:06.610 --> 35:07.983
My father saw him severely injured,

35:08.130 --> 35:09.090
so he healed him

35:09.130 --> 35:10.340
and showed him a way out.

35:10.980 --> 35:12.050
Since then, Mr. Chang

35:12.050 --> 35:13.980
has remembered my father's kindness

35:14.610 --> 35:15.690
and promised

35:16.300 --> 35:17.530
that if I were ever in danger,

35:18.300 --> 35:19.530
he'd protect me.

35:24.010 --> 35:25.490
Uncle Chang has always been grateful.

35:26.860 --> 35:28.420
That's indeed something he'd do.

35:30.210 --> 35:31.050
A year ago,

35:31.880 --> 35:33.753
Nie Zhe wiped out
the remnants of the Mu clan,

35:34.090 --> 35:36.090
claiming he killed the Young Master.

35:36.340 --> 35:37.420
Was the poison on you

35:38.610 --> 35:39.900
left then?

35:40.050 --> 35:41.843
The Li Sect has always belonged
to my family.

35:42.650 --> 35:43.940
After Nie Hengcheng died,

35:44.820 --> 35:45.940
Nie Zhe wanted to take over,

35:46.300 --> 35:47.350
so he couldn't tolerate me.

35:47.860 --> 35:49.050
He seriously injured me.

35:55.610 --> 35:56.900
Nie Zhe practiced the Wudu Palm.

35:57.530 --> 35:58.370
I couldn't beat him.

35:58.370 --> 36:00.340
(Nie Zhe, Chief of Li Sect)

36:03.260 --> 36:04.100
Then,

36:04.340 --> 36:05.690
I escaped to Chang Fort.

36:33.900 --> 36:34.740
Here.

36:56.980 --> 36:58.130
He kept his promise

36:58.650 --> 36:59.776
and protected me to the end.

37:01.570 --> 37:03.260
The Chang Fort saved my life.

37:04.490 --> 37:05.780
When I return to Li Sect,

37:06.260 --> 37:07.420
I'll strip Nie Zhe

37:08.340 --> 37:09.780
and the Demonic Camp

37:11.260 --> 37:12.420
to the bones.

37:14.900 --> 37:15.740
Enough.

37:16.260 --> 37:17.650
That's your demon sect business.

37:18.210 --> 37:19.090
Give me the antidote.

37:19.740 --> 37:20.580
From now on,

37:20.780 --> 37:21.900
we go

37:22.340 --> 37:23.420
our separate ways.

37:23.740 --> 37:24.780
Zhao, you want

37:25.490 --> 37:26.570
to cut ties with me?

37:27.050 --> 37:28.380
Luoying Valley isn't just mine.

37:28.940 --> 37:29.813
It belongs to my aunt,

37:29.980 --> 37:31.510
my father, my mother,

37:31.530 --> 37:32.940
and countless valley residents.

37:33.610 --> 37:34.789
I can't selfishly

37:34.800 --> 37:36.130
let the whole valley be accused

37:36.130 --> 37:37.530
of colluding with the demon sect.

37:37.900 --> 37:38.940
Collude all you want.

37:40.130 --> 37:41.490
Just bring the entire valley over

37:41.940 --> 37:42.940
if you like.

37:43.490 --> 37:44.490
Like Qianmian Sect?

37:45.050 --> 37:46.610
Ending up with total destruction?

37:49.806 --> 37:51.472
Since you refuse
to give me the antidote,

37:53.820 --> 37:55.310
if something happens to Qian Xueshen,

37:55.570 --> 37:56.460
it's his fate.

38:01.460 --> 38:02.300
Let's go.

38:02.780 --> 38:03.746
Do we have the antidote?

38:07.840 --> 38:08.780
Take three pills a day

38:09.020 --> 38:10.100
for three consecutive days.

38:25.940 --> 38:26.980
The snow mountains are

38:26.980 --> 38:28.213
at least a thousand miles away.

38:28.530 --> 38:29.940
Even riding fast,

38:29.951 --> 38:31.010
without eating or drinking,

38:31.050 --> 38:32.260
it'll take dozens of days.

38:32.570 --> 38:33.780
Better take my Golden Peng.

38:34.146 --> 38:35.210
You'll arrive in two days.

38:35.260 --> 38:36.480
Ride a bird?

38:36.820 --> 38:38.090
What if we fall?

38:38.650 --> 38:39.856
This is an ancient Golden Peng.

38:41.740 --> 38:43.780
With all this threatening and bribing,

38:44.490 --> 38:45.330
what do you want?

38:45.650 --> 38:46.596
I'm worried about you.

38:47.130 --> 38:48.260
I want to go with you.

38:48.460 --> 38:49.820
- No.
- Then stay another night.

38:50.690 --> 38:52.090
We've shared a room for so long.

38:52.740 --> 38:54.380
Surely, there's some trust left.

38:54.610 --> 38:56.340
You shared a room?

39:05.761 --> 39:16.421
=Generation to Generation=

39:35.181 --> 39:39.591
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

39:40.156 --> 39:44.771
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

39:45.111 --> 39:49.676
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

39:50.201 --> 39:54.501
♪Free to wander in the world♪

39:57.446 --> 40:02.146
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:02.671 --> 40:06.961
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

40:07.621 --> 40:11.651
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

40:11.966 --> 40:17.091
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

40:17.666 --> 40:22.476
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:22.691 --> 40:26.861
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

40:27.586 --> 40:31.521
♪I freely roam in the world♪

40:32.021 --> 40:37.296
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

